=== TEST 1: the tcp_check test
--- http_config
    upstream test{
        server 127.0.0.1:1970;
        server 127.0.0.1:1971;
        server 127.0.0.1:1972;

        check interval=3000 rise=1 fall=1 timeout=1000;
    }

    server {
        listen 1970;

        location / {
            root   html;
            index  index.html index.htm;
        }
    }

--- config
    location / {
        proxy_pass http://test;
    }

--- request
GET /
--- response_body_like: ^<(.*)>$

